com.camerontec.catalys.server.sessionmanager

Interface ISessionManagerListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EventListener, ICatalysEventListener, ISessionStatusEventListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SampleMonitor, SessionConfigurationMXBeanImpl, SessionConfigurationMXBeanSpecificImpl, SessionMXBeanImpl, SessionStatusListenerBase, SolaceMessageSource

    public interface ISessionManagerListener
extends ISessionStatusEventListener
    Listeners to SessionManager's should implement this interface.

    Since a SessionManager passes on all the events of its associated Session, a SessionManager listener is also a Session listener.
